summary: Alexandre Lacazette (Arsenal): "I'm finally in the final" of Europa League
title: Alexandre Lacazette (Arsenal): "I'm finally in the final" of Europa League
body:
Eliminated in the semi-finals of the Europa League in 2017 (with Lyon) and in 2018, Alexandre Lacazette will play the final of the competition with Arsenal for his greatest happiness.


Alexandre Lacazette (Arsenal striker, at the microphone of RMC Sport): “We have a chance to play the next Champions League but above all, we have a chance to win a trophy! We have been regular in the Europa League. It’s almost perfect match, even though we conceded two goals. We knew they were going to put a lot of pressure, we knew how to calm the game, to equalize rather quickly and to control afterwards. Last year, we had failed at the gates of the final against Atlético, and here I am finally! The advantage of the go was enough. ”

Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang (Arsenal striker, at the microphone of BT Sport): “We learned from our mistakes of last season. It is a pleasure to play with Alexandre Lacazette, especially when everything is going well as was the case tonight (Thursday). ”

title: Wognum heeft ‘eigen’ paard tijdens 54ste kortebaandraverij
body:
WOGNUM – Voor de Stichting Kortebaandraverij Wognum wordt de 54ste koers over de Kerkstraat mogelijk extra spannend. De organisatie doet mee aan de Super Vrienden-actie van Kortebaandraverijen.nl en is daardoor mede-eigenaar van de paarden Emi van Jip en Gaya Vip. De kans is groot dat één van deze merries op vrijdag 31 mei aan de start verschijnt. De aanvang is 13.00 uur. De eerste start valt…
